  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the World of Godly Survivors!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace yourself for an electrifying action rogue-lite experience, where the only way out is to obliterate hordes of menacing mobs. Harness the powers of the gods, level up unique heroes, and break free from a never-ending cycle of combat. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supercharge your gameplay with a vast array of runtime skills. Max them out and become a <strong>hero with unstoppable force</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/cb3970c9018535111d928a909d27e645.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/cb3970c9018535111d928a909d27e645.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/cb3970c9018535111d928a909d27e645.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerup Tree</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest souls in your <strong>Powerup Tree</strong> to unlock and enhance more than <strong>10 unique skills</strong>. Transform your hero into a powerhouse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/975b701a87765df66b104798efe2176d.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/975b701a87765df66b104798efe2176d.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/975b701a87765df66b104798efe2176d.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Fighter: Exclusive Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of characters, each with unique abilities to help you achieve victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/9a917854a0fe28b1a0617bb6f84a37b6.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/9a917854a0fe28b1a0617bb6f84a37b6.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/9a917854a0fe28b1a0617bb6f84a37b6.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Favor of the Gods: Altars & Temples</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gods are on your side! Utilize <strong>mystical altars and temples</strong> to gain divine blessings and navigate the challenges ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/c64e546118d75f3f8bebe785910f6481.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/c64e546118d75f3f8bebe785910f6481.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/c64e546118d75f3f8bebe785910f6481.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We Want to Hear YOU!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’m a developer who values creating games that bring joy and excitement. Your feedback is incredibly important to me because it helps shape the game into something you want to play. Together, we can create something truly special!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for joining us on this epic adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The battleground awaits - will you rise to the challenge?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the World of Godly Survivors!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace yourself for an electrifying action rogue-lite experience, where the only way out is to obliterate hordes of menacing mobs. Harness the powers of the gods, level up unique heroes, and break free from a never-ending cycle of combat. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supercharge your gameplay with a vast array of runtime skills. Max them out and become a <strong>hero with unstoppable force</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/cb3970c9018535111d928a909d27e645.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/cb3970c9018535111d928a909d27e645.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/cb3970c9018535111d928a909d27e645.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerup Tree</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest souls in your <strong>Powerup Tree</strong> to unlock and enhance more than <strong>10 unique skills</strong>. Transform your hero into a powerhouse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/975b701a87765df66b104798efe2176d.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/975b701a87765df66b104798efe2176d.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/975b701a87765df66b104798efe2176d.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Fighter: Exclusive Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of characters, each with unique abilities to help you achieve victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/9a917854a0fe28b1a0617bb6f84a37b6.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/9a917854a0fe28b1a0617bb6f84a37b6.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/9a917854a0fe28b1a0617bb6f84a37b6.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Favor of the Gods: Altars & Temples</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gods are on your side! Utilize <strong>mystical altars and temples</strong> to gain divine blessings and navigate the challenges ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/c64e546118d75f3f8bebe785910f6481.poster.avif?t=1737476767\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/c64e546118d75f3f8bebe785910f6481.webm?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625680/extras/c64e546118d75f3f8bebe785910f6481.mp4?t=1737476767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We Want to Hear YOU!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’m a developer who values creating games that bring joy and excitement. Your feedback is incredibly important to me because it helps shape the game into something you want to play. Together, we can create something truly special!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for joining us on this epic adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The battleground awaits - will you rise to the challenge?</strong></p>",
